{"tid":506410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男保安：游蕙禎膝蓋碰到我大腿3至4次","createTime":"2017-12-22T07:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T16:31:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"33cc1ba587e52a8ec7eb7f0fde7a087d0b62806b","tid":506410,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"青年新政前立法會議員梁頌恆、游蕙禎及其三名助理被指硬闖立會會議室案，<br />\n男保安員張瑞成供稱，案發時他在會議室門口伸開雙臂封鎖門框位置，游蕙禎一隻腳伸入保安員與保安員之間的空隙試圖衝破防線，其間游的膝蓋碰到他大腿3至4次，他認為游是故意的。"},{"pid":"a9f2e1f695aaecc2160e50b0e0cdba4dcd69f3db","tid":506410,"uid":2313,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f2727b1c391a59169871cd01552855c76d0217","tid":506410,"uid":139613,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"臭G"},{"pid":"fbb21bfbc45d99e28017a80af18c8f512ac6a161","tid":506410,"uid":8949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"下段踢？"},{"pid":"16702e87daf8f1e67d262d4d83f7472de68a2ee3","tid":506410,"uid":22553,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"磨大腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇射到一地都係"},{"pid":"4b3c188085cceeac0e1fd2507f0090ba1b222069","tid":506410,"uid":4783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"惟辯方律師譚俊傑質疑張在庭上的供詞與事發8天後提供的口供紀錄有出入，張亦同意當時沒提及是因看見鍾的紅色衣袖及手部動作才判斷張是搥打他的人，但否認自己「搞錯咗」。張事後因不感疼痛、又無紅腫的表面傷痕，所以未有求診或驗傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1095467/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1095467%2F&d=c9o%2Bp0wmVt%2Bykjwp0NVuhxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=904f0231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.k